Butterknife provisioning server tools
=====================================

The overlay/ directory contains files intended to be installed on the machine
that will be used to serve templates.

Install dependencies:

    sudo apt-get install python3-pip python3-lxc pigz btrfs-progs
    sudo pip3 install falcon==0.2.0b1

To start the Butterknife server:

    sudo python3 /usr/share/butterknife/server/api.py
